row_m4.layer_m4_ctx.sha256_ctx -> row_m4.layer_m4_nist.nist_v2: "produces digest"
row_m4.layer_m4_ctx.sha256_ctx -> row_m4.layer_m4_nist.nist_v3: "produces digest"
